SUMMARY:LAW OF ATTRACTION: Live the Life You Truly Wish To Live! (Sunday M
 arch 29th) 
DESCRIPTION:Try New Things in Toronto!\nHello everyone\,\n\nPlease join us
  for an inspiring\, interactive and insightful afternoon as we continue to
  move closer to living the life we wish to live using the amazing and mira
 culous Law of Attraction.\n\nWe're going to have a lot of fun too!\n\n\\*J
 oined by my other personal growth and social groups too\; so we can antici
 pate a terrific turn out\, with wonderful like minded people\n\n**Date:**\
 nSunday\, March 29th 2026\n**Arrival Time:**\nArrive between 4:00 pm and 4
 :30 pm\n**Where to Meet us?**\n**Location: La Carnita - Good Fortune Bar (
 Main Floor)**\n**Address:** 130 Eglinton Ave. Toronto\, ON M4P 2X9\n**Free
  Parking:** on Eglinton and Residential area\n**Yonge and Eglinton Subway:
 ** (Very close\, 3 minute walking distance)\n\nEvent Details below:\n\nSin
 cerely\,\n\nSteve Flemming\n(Organizer/Host)\n\n\\-\\-\\-\nEvent Details:\
 n**LAW OF ATTRACTION: Live the Life You Truly Wish To Live!**\n**(Sunday\,
  March 29th)**\n\n-Take your life to the next level with increased clarity
 \, joy\, fulfillment\, abundance and peace\n-Deepen your understanding on 
 how to apply the **Law of Attraction** so it works in all areas of your li
 fe (Personal\, Professional\, Social & Romantic)\n-Develop your confidence
  and sense of self so you are more open to receive what the universe wants
  to give you\n-Tap into your inner source of passions\, talents and creati
 vity that will guide you to a life beyond your wildest imagination *(And t
 hen ask the Universe for even more!)*\n\n\\*Interactive\, inspiring and in
 sightful afternoon designed to help you live the life you truly desire and
  truly deserve to live (with greater flow\, energy\, ease and purpose)\n\n
 \\*This event will be effectively facilitated with powerful insights\, use
 ful tools\, practical exercises and group participation\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-
 \\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n***Our Instructor/Facili
 tator:***\n**Steve Flemming** is the founder of **Soul City Social Club si
 nce 2006.** He produces monthly events on subjects involving personal/spir
 itual growth\, modern dating and healthy relationships while incorporating
  the **Law of Attraction and other useful tools.** Each event is designed 
 to help you experience greater joy\, inner peace\, confidence\, fulfillmen
 t\, love\, meaning and aliveness in our lives. Steve is a professional gro
 up Facilitator and Inspirational Speaker. Steve has an ongoing passion to 
 help shift people's lives and consciousness for the better in areas that m
 atter most to you.\nhttps://www.meetup.com/SoulCity/\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\
 -\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\
 \-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n*
 *When to arrive: (Ask for Steve when you arrive-or head to back area)**\n-
 Please arrive between 4:00 pm and 4:30 pm (to get registered and settled i
 n)\n-The formal part of the afternoon will start shortly after 4:30 p.m. a
 nd go until roughly 6:30 p.m.\n-Stick around after for more mingling and o
 ur dinner party (optional)\n\\*no extra charge for attending the dinner pa
 rty event\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-
 \\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\
 -\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n\n**Event Fee:** 10 dollars upon arrival (HST include
 d)\n(Cash only when you arrive or in advance by e transfer to- steveflemmi
 ng11@gmail.com\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\n\\*Lunch/Dinner & Beverage Menu available 
 too\n\\*Includes reserved seating for the group\n\\*At least one Beverage 
 and/or appetizer minimum to support the staff and venue\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\
 -\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n**Parking Available:
 **\n\\*Plenty of free street parking on Eglinton and (Residential area sou
 th/east of venue for free)\n**Close to Subway Station:**\n\\*Also very clo
 se to the the Yonge/Eglinton subway station\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-
